Template: borhan-nginx/nginx_hostname
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Server name

Template: borhan-nginx/nginx_port
Type: string
Default: 88
Description: Vhost port to listen on:

Template: borhan-nginx/rtmp_port
Type: string
Default: 1935
Description: RTMP port to listen on:

Template: borhan-nginx/nginx_ssl_port
Type: string
Default: 8443
Description: Vhost SSL port to listen on:

Template: borhan-nginx/borhan_service_url
Type: string
Default:
Description: Your Borhan Service URL:
	Base URL where the Borhan API will be accessed from - this would be your Load Balancer URL on a cluster or same as your virtual host in an all-in-one Borhan server.
	Note that currently, only HTTP is supported and make sure to insert the host without the http:// prefix.

Template: borhan-nginx/ssl_cert
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Please input path to your SSL certificate:

Template: borhan-nginx/ssl_key
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Please input path to your SSL key:

Template: borhan-nginx/is_ssl
Type: boolean
Default: 
Description: Config Nginx with SSL?

